---
<!-- Hero: copy + registration form on the LEFT, iPad image on the RIGHT
     (the homepage newsletter / watchlist split layout). -->
<section class="bf-section bf-hero bf-hero--dark" id="register">
  <div
    class="bf-hero-dots"
    data-dotgrid
    data-dot-size="2"
    data-gap="10"
    data-base-color="#454545"
    data-active-color="#75B5FF"
    data-proximity="140"
    data-return-duration="0.6"
  ></div>
  <div class="bf-hero-scrim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="bf-container">
    <div class="bf-newsletter-split">
      <div class="bf-newsletter-split__copy">
        <h1 class="bf-h1">Learn how to trade the opening hour with a repeatable options plan</h1>
        <p class="bf-lead" style="margin-top:22px">In under 60 minutes, see the exact rules Bill uses to trade the first hour of the market. You walk away with a routine you can practice the next morning. No hype, no hot tips. Just a rules-based way to place trades, define your downside, and skip the mistakes that drain most retail accounts.</p>
        <div class="bf-newsletter-split__form">
          <SubscribeForm
            id="wf-form-Webinar-form"
            name="wf-form-Webinar-form"
            dataName="Webinar form"
            redirect="https://www.billfanter.com/watch-webinar"
            wfPageId="664c1c1ece7e660fcaf8ed86"
            wfElementId="eb9cc3d0-5bee-f6c7-958c-fe96d382d256"
            turnstileSitekey="0x4AAAAAAAQTptj2So4dx43e"
            nameField="LM-name"
            nameDataName="LM name"
            nameRequired={false}
            emailField="LM-email"
            emailDataName="LM email"
            submitLabel="Watch Now"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bf-newsletter-split__media bf-webinar-media">
        <img
          src="/assets/664a5b263659c7265be280ad/664a67e56ac2f27a7b0c898e_home%20images-2.webp"
          alt="Bill Fanter webinar shown on an iPad"
          sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px"
          fetchpriority="high"
          srcset="/assets/664a5b263659c7265be280ad/664a67e56ac2f27a7b0c898e_home%20images-2-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/664a5b263659c7265be280ad/664a67e56ac2f27a7b0c898e_home%20images-2-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/664a5b263659c7265be280ad/664a67e56ac2f27a7b0c898e_home%20images-2-p-1080.webp 1080w, /assets/664a5b263659c7265be280ad/664a67e56ac2f27a7b0c898e_home%20images-2.webp 1524w"
        />
        <!-- Rotating trust tags, top-right of the image: one shows at a time and
             cross-fades to the next in sequence. -->
        <div class="bf-webinar-tags" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="bf-webinar-tag">35-year finance pro; $10B+ overseen</span>
          <span class="bf-webinar-tag">1,200+ students taught</span>
          <span class="bf-webinar-tag">1,000+ traders in our community</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Before you place another trade… — WHITE bg. homepage HelpGrid rhythm:
     centered header → framed full-width media → even feature-card grid → CTA. -->
<section class="bf-section">
  <div class="bf-container">
    <div class="bf-section-header is-center">
      <h2 class="bf-h2">Before you place another options trade, see how Bill reads and trades the opening hour</h2>
      <p class="bf-lead">The first hour of the trading day moves fast, and most traders react instead of trading a plan. In this free options webinar, Bill walks through how he reads the open and defines his risk before he places a trade, so you can run the same routine with your own account.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bf-community-grid">
      <div class="bf-community__media">
        <img
          src="/assets/664a5b263659c7265be280ad/68540f8f0903fae1504f6a44_SS.webp"
          alt="Bill Fanter's live trading community on Discord"
          sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px"
          loading="lazy"
          srcset="/assets/664a5b263659c7265be280ad/68540f8f0903fae1504f6a44_SS-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/664a5b263659c7265be280ad/68540f8f0903fae1504f6a44_SS-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/664a5b263659c7265be280ad/68540f8f0903fae1504f6a44_SS-p-1080.webp 1080w, /assets/664a5b263659c7265be280ad/68540f8f0903fae1504f6a44_SS.webp 1860w"
